==== ENTRY 6 ====
HEADWORD: Mete
<hw>Mete</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS. <ets>met</ets>. See <er>Mete</er>
to measure.]</ety> <def>Measure; limit; boundary; -- used chiefly in the
plural, and in the phrase <xex>metes and bounds</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

